CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 9, 1958, pg. A20, reads: "Harper and Pretties - Bandleader Walt Harper, who scored sensationally at the Frogs' formal at Gateway Plaza last week, took time out to pose with this group of pretty ladies who congratulated the band. Left to right: Mrs. Lois Watson, Mrs. Frances Nunn, Harper, Mrs. Mabel Bookert and Mrs. Phyllis Pitts. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Lois Weaver Watson, Frances Bell Nunn, Walt Harper, Mabel Bookert, and Phyllis Pitts, standing in front of landscape mural, for FROGS formal, Gateway Plaza
